WITH patient_stays AS (
    SELECT 
        p.patientunitstayid,
        p.uniquepid,
        p.hospitaladmittime
    FROM 
        patient p
    WHERE 
        p.uniquepid = '031-4987'
),
last_hospital_stay AS (
    SELECT 
        patientunitstayid
    FROM 
        patient_stays
    ORDER BY 
        hospitaladmittime DESC
    LIMIT 1
),
first_blood_test AS (
    SELECT 
        m.organism,
        m.culturetakentime
    FROM 
        microlab m
    JOIN 
        last_hospital_stay lhs ON m.patientunitstayid = lhs.patientunitstayid
    WHERE 
        m.culturesite LIKE 'blood%'
        AND m.culturesite LIKE '%venipuncture%'
    ORDER BY 
        m.culturetakentime ASC
    LIMIT 1
)
SELECT 
    organism
FROM 
    first_blood_test;

input: what is the minimum total cost of a hospital, including a procedure called bronchodilator - leukotriene receptor antagonists?

SELECT 
    p.hospitalid, 
    SUM(c.cost) AS total_cost
FROM 
    patient p
JOIN 
    medication m ON p.patientunitstayid = m.patientunitstayid
JOIN 
    cost c ON p.uniquepid = c.uniquepid 
            AND p.patienthealthsystemstayid = c.patienthealthsystemstayid 
            AND c.eventtype = 'medication' 
            AND c.eventid = m.medicationid
WHERE 
    LOWER(m.drugname) LIKE '%bronchodilator - leukotriene receptor antagonist%'
GROUP BY 
    p.hospitalid
ORDER BY 
    total_cost ASC
LIMIT 1;

JOIN medication m2 ON m1.patientunitstayid = m2.patientunitstayid
WHERE m1.drugname = 'allopurinol'
  AND m1.dosage = '100 mg'
  AND m1.routeadmin = 'po'
  AND m2.drugname != 'allopurinol'
  AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM m1.drugstarttime) = 2105
  AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM m2.drugstarttime) = 2105
  AND (
    (m2.drugstarttime BETWEEN m1.drugstarttime AND COALESCE(m1.drugstoptime, '2105-12-31 23:59:59')) OR
    (m2.drugstoptime BETWEEN m1.drugstarttime AND COALESCE(m1.drugstoptime, '2105-12-31 23:59:59')) OR
    (m1.drugstarttime BETWEEN m2.drugstarttime AND COALESCE(m2.drugstoptime, '2105-12-31 23:59:59')) OR
    (m1.drugstoptime BETWEEN m2.drugstarttime AND COALESCE(m2.drugstoptime, '2105-12-31 23:59:59'))
  )
GROUP BY m2.drugname
ORDER BY prescription_count DESC
LIMIT 5;
